    <section id="id9004931">
      <title>1.Christian Holy day</title>
      <para id="id8983234">Celebrating special days on the religious calendar is a very important part of our life. It is almost the same as celebrating one’s birthday. Here is a list of some of the important holy days celebrated by four of the most prominent religious communities in South Africa.</para>
