      <section id="id9403068">
        <title>[LO 2.5]</title>
        <para id="id7959225">Pick a religious festival that is important to you or that is celebrated by your family. Explain or demonstrate to the rest of the learners what you do on that day. It would be effective if you made use of a little tableau to demonstrate the rituals. If you do not observe any holy days, you may find it interesting to read up on one of the above-mentioned festivals.</para>
      </section>
